{"tid":2252824,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經］一人一個讀書年代印象深刻既同學/老師","createTime":"2020-10-21T17:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T09:29:25.000Z","uid":159697,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"11057273825a90a0278157b6580c486fbf21dfc6","tid":2252824,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:32:11.000Z","msg":"讀小學個陣有個上音樂堂學牧童笛<br />\n每次教完首歌 大家練習既時候如果有人唔專心/彈錯既話 佢就會暴走崩潰喊住鬧全班 話我地成班都係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家諗返真係覺得佢好撚癲 好似有情緒病<br />\n<br />\n讀中學有個同學會食人二手飯<br />\n唔知太窮定咩 佢會食哂成枱人食剩既二手飯就當一餐lunch 比人笑都唔care 真心幾高eq<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f358ba9ce03bb8399e3ea44f85e047f601b299d3","tid":2252824,"uid":189235,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:34:53.000Z","msg":"有個呀蛇會要人叫佢the most handsome teacher in school<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a7b9f9c0631eac88424cb99690dd4bad90c741","tid":2252824,"uid":266145,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:40:42.000Z","msg":"有個小學老師話自己日日放工都入迪士尼睇煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df38613caba94dfcd55ba751ec37ffcb0d06e21","tid":2252824,"uid":251269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f358ba9ce03bb8399e3ea44f85e047f601b299d3","tid":2252824,"uid":189235,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:34:53.000Z","msg":"有個呀蛇會要人叫佢the most handsome teacher in school<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:46:42.000Z","msg":"我小學都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3dca601bd3a5e998cc8ed240f76b2c126a8582","tid":2252824,"uid":233873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T17:53:06.000Z","msg":"小學有個唔太受歡迎既圖